title: ‘Survivor’ Season 41 Finale
description:
Tyson and Riley are joined by four-time ‘Survivor’ contestant Cirie Fields to discuss the finale and Season 41 at large. They break down what may be the best fire-making challenge ever and share stories from their respective seasons. Plus, they react to the final tribal council and look ahead to Season 42.
Hosts: Tyson Apostol and Riley McAtee
Guest: Cirie Fields
Associate Producer: Mike Wargon
